  "keyFeatures": [
    "Error monitoring and exception tracking across all JavaScript platforms",
    "Performance monitoring with distributed tracing and OpenTelemetry",
    "40+ platform-specific SDKs (Browser, Node, React, Vue, Next.js, etc.)",
    "AI monitoring integrations (OpenAI, Anthropic, LangChain, Vercel AI)",
    "Session replay with canvas recording",
    "Profiling for Node.js applications",
    "User feedback collection",
    "Feature flags integration",
    "Breadcrumbs and context management",
    "Serverless and edge runtime support"
